### 短链接服务 API 测试

### 1. 创建短链接
POST http://localhost:8081/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "original_url": "https://example.com/very/long/url/that/needs/to/be/shortened"
}

### 2. 访问短链接（会重定向）
GET http://localhost:8081/DwHqrL

### 3. 获取访问统计
GET http://localhost:8081/abc123/stats

### 4. 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8081/healthz

### 5. 就绪检查
GET http://localhost:8081/readyz

### 6.删除短链接
DELETE http://localhost:8081/DwHqrL
